(38, 'Introducing The Final 9 Members Of “Girl’s Planet 999″‘s Girl Group: Kep1er', 'introducing-the-final-9-members-of-“girl’s-planet-999″‘s-girl-group:-kep1er-02-11-2021', '<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<div class=\"header-rest-of\">\r\n<div class=\"header-excerpt\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Here&rsquo;s who made it through to the final lineup of Kep1er! Did your pick make the cut?</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"featured-image-container has-fi-source\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"assets/images/content/34/b9c2889fd3ae06d9c9148b68a4e0d681670b6aef.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"504\" /></div>\r\n<div class=\"entry-meta grid-parent\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"writer-bio grid-parent\">\r\n<div class=\"posted-on\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">The finale episode of&nbsp;<strong>Mnet</strong>&lsquo;s survival show&nbsp;<em>Girls Planet 999</em>&nbsp;is over, which means the winners have finally been decided! Here are all nine members of new girl group&nbsp;<strong>Kep1er</strong>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"kb-ads-once\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-init=\"Koreaboo_Teads\" data-tag=\"Koreaboo_Between_Article\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h1 style=\"text-align: justify;\">9. Shen Xiaoting</h1>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Shen Xiaoting of C-Group (<strong>TOP Class Entertainment</strong>) is the 9th member of Kep1er with 700,663 points from voters.</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"lazyload-ph lazyload no-js-hide alignnone size-full wp-image-1143315 k-image\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/tuHehsWRxf6K0MNDjfj8sZUrcOepaTrAU-9_HyhD-nAITxNbReDTYG_u07u_vXn3Hne1o8k9utEUaqSUlShp8hHYd3kkPbvSg55ivWLzZ6t8tg=w32-fSoften=1,100,0-rp-e365\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 765px\" srcset=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/tuHehsWRxf6K0MN