(47, 'BLACKPINK’s Lisa, aespa’s Winter, ONEUS’s Seoho And More Idols Wore The Same “Squid Game” Halloween Outfit, But Served Completely Different Spooky Vibes', 'blackpink’s-lisa,-aespa’s-winter,-oneus’s-seoho-and-more-idols-wore-the-same-“squid-game”-halloween-outfit,-but-served-completely-different-spooky-vibes-02-11-2021', '<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<div class=\"header-rest-of\">\r\n<div class=\"header-excerpt\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">They each had their own &ldquo;creepy&rdquo; interpretations!</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"featured-image-container\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"entry-meta grid-parent\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"writer-bio grid-parent\">\r\n<div class=\"posted-on\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"assets/images/content/46/e542d5d4e5435537d2fefe92e58c046b4ebd2c55.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"884\" height=\"464\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">When Halloween comes around, there is no denying that the K-Pop industry goes into overload. From&nbsp;<strong>SM Entertainment</strong>&lsquo;s&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.koreaboo.com/lists/smtown-wonderland-halloween-party-2021-costumes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Halloween Party</a>&nbsp;to themed dance practices, each year, fans wait in anticipation to see what idols will be dressing up as!</p>\r\n<div class=\"kb-ads-once\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-init=\"Koreaboo_Teads\" data-tag=\"Koreaboo_Between_Article\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Each year, a different craze takes over the holiday, and with its success, it seems like the&nbsp;</span><strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Netflix</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;series&nbsp;</span><em><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Squid Game</span></em><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">&nbsp;was a huge inspiration for costumes this year. In particular, the outfit for the creepy doll&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.koreaboo.com/stories/inspiration-creepy-doll-squid-game/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Younghee</a>!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_1149460\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"lazyload-ph lazyload no-js-hide wp-image-1149460 size-full k-image\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0QgvvLroK=w32-fSoften=1,100,0-rp-e365\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 765px\" srcset=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0QgvvLroK=w480-rj-l80-nu-e365 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0QgvvLroK=w640-rj-l80-nu-e365 640w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0QgvvLroK=w780-rj-l80-nu-e365 780w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0QgvvLroK=w960-rj-l80-nu-e365 960w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0QgvvLroK=w1200-rj-l80-nu-e365 1200w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0QgvvLroK=w1600-rj-l80-nu-e365 1600w\" data-alt=\"unnamed\" data-orig=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/hiWDB_f_9X9GA7buXmdD2BfBf2STzB8pj7EWFPNt3p23WG9MQ79X044YjmyqVRepro0-x9Z0-98vw82XWdsVu9eCQwClu_VZBrbvGHK0Q