reserver-spaces=\"true\">&lsquo;s&nbsp;</span><strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">Lisa</span></strong><span data-preserver-spaces=\"true\">. With her short hair and statement red lips, Lisa definitely brought a stylish twist to the look with her visuals, making a very scary costume seem gorgeous!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_1149464\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"lazyload-ph lazyload no-js-hide wp-image-1149464 size-full k-image\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6wcT-3rX3-R5PlxBQ8oFU6D_JImmNm8pPaq7eAxCwHLOurn=w32-fSoften=1,100,0-rp-e365\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 765px\" srcset=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6wcT-3rX3-R5PlxBQ8oFU6D_JImmNm8pPaq7eAxCwHLOurn=w480-rj-l80-nu-e365 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6wcT-3rX3-R5PlxBQ8oFU6D_JImmNm8pPaq7eAxCwHLOurn=w640-rj-l80-nu-e365 640w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6wcT-3rX3-R5PlxBQ8oFU6D_JImmNm8pPaq7eAxCwHLOurn=w780-rj-l80-nu-e365 780w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6wcT-3rX3-R5PlxBQ8oFU6D_JImmNm8pPaq7eAxCwHLOurn=w960-rj-l80-nu-e365 960w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6wcT-3rX3-R5PlxBQ8oFU6D_JImmNm8pPaq7eAxCwHLOurn=w1200-rj-l80-nu-e365 1200w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6wcT-3rX3-R5PlxBQ8oFU6D_JImmNm8pPaq7eAxCwHLOurn=w1600-rj-l80-nu-e365 1600w\" data-alt=\"FDBrEz2XMAE3YL0\" data-orig=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/GMNI4X-B4bVUNC81a4G-G2IoiZzxSBrSFyJAZT9lTTtxJatIVJU7Ud8Zex7xW8VxG6w