(54, 'The Wholesome Story Of BTS V’s First Time On An Airplane, Eight Years Ago', 'the-wholesome-story-of-bts-v’s-first-time-on-an-airplane,-eight-years-ago-02-11-2021', '<header class=\"entry-header\">\r\n<div class=\"header-rest-of\">\r\n<div class=\"header-excerpt\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">He&rsquo;s grown so much since then.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"entry-meta grid-parent\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"writer-bio grid-parent\">\r\n<div class=\"posted-on\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"assets/images/content/52/83ba2b460f286b56ff5c9c42e2a9bf10e67d3dc1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</header>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Now that&nbsp;<strong>BTS&nbsp;</strong>are frequently traveling around the globe for world tours and international events, it might be hard to think about a time when they hadn&rsquo;t even been on a plane. But almost eight years ago, that was the case for&nbsp;<strong>V</strong>!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_1150379\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img class=\"lazyload-ph lazyload no-js-hide wp-image-1150379 size-full k-image\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/dr5Krxmd5WLfLR3VGLrpR3jSEWRcPR3DKItwVMof8JPzkjvtleqFXZfRLRbNb9Mroxb-g33koy3Mq67jinmSLuaMSA70SrAcGgSm4jG7raMtoQ=w32-fSoften=1,100,0-rp-e365\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 765px\" srcset=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/dr5Krxmd5WLfLR3VGLrpR3jSEWRcPR3DKItwVMof8JPzkjvtleqFXZfRLRbNb9Mroxb-g33koy3Mq67jinmSLuaMSA70SrAcGgSm4jG7raMtoQ=w480-rj-l80-nu-e365 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/dr5Krxmd5WLfLR3VGLrpR3jSEWRcPR3DKItwVMof8JPzkjvtleqFXZfRLRbNb9Mroxb-g33koy3Mq67jinmSLuaMSA70SrAcGgSm4jG7raMtoQ=w640-rj-l80-nu-e365 640w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/dr5Krxmd5WLfLR3VGLrpR3jSEWRcPR3DKItwVMof8JPzkjvtleqFXZfRLRbN