(58, 'The “Squid Game” Scene That Made Heo Sung Tae “Shake In Fear” While Filming', 'the-“squid-game”-scene-that-made-heo-sung-tae-“shake-in-fear”-while-filming-02-11-2021', '<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">This just proves how amazing his acting skills are!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"assets/images/content/58/cfe07f75f9af68c046f048dcb6b64b7f661a8084.jpeg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Last month,&nbsp;<em>Squid Game</em>&lsquo;s&nbsp;<strong>Heo Sung Tae&nbsp;</strong>(who played Jang Deok Su) revealed that the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.koreaboo.com/news/squid-game-actors-hardest-scene/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">tug of war scene</a>&nbsp;was the&nbsp;<em>hardest</em>&nbsp;to shoot because of all the effort they had to put into pulling the rope. Now, the actor has confessed which scene was the&nbsp;<em>scariest</em>.</p>\r\n<div class=\"kb-ads-once\" style=\"text-align: justify;\" data-init=\"Koreaboo_Teads\" data-tag=\"Koreaboo_Between_Article\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">A few days ago, Heo Sung Tae guest-starred on&nbsp;<strong>SBS</strong>&lsquo;s&nbsp;<em>My Little Old Boy&nbsp;</em>to talk about his rise to fame and time on&nbsp;<em>Squid Game</em>. Alongside hilariously confessing that his mom loved seeing his&nbsp;<strong>Instagram</strong>&nbsp;following grow from 10,000 to 2.2 million, Heo also revealed that fans find him scary when they see him in public because of his role as Jang Deok Su.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_1150208\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"lazyload-ph lazyload no-js-hide wp-image-1150208 size-full k-image\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w32-fSoften=1,100,0-rp-e365\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 765px\" srcset=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w480-rj-l80-nu-e365 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w640-rj-l80-nu-e365 640w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w780-rj-l80-nu-e365 780w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w960-rj-l80-nu-e365 960w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w1200-rj-l80-nu-e365 1200w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w1600-rj-l80-nu-e365 1600w\" data-alt=\"hstscared_1\" data-orig=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=s0-e365\" data-placeholder=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w32-fSoften=1,100,0-rp-e365\" data-srcset=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w480-rj-l80-nu-e365 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w640-rj-l80-nu-e365 640w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w780-rj-l80-nu-e365 780w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w960-rj-l80-nu-e365 960w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w1200-rj-l80-nu-e365 1200w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LaiKVK1BeMUH3vGqxztwroeFq0Ugk0Zzj7tRgdxnx8V3QdgCtE4Ghwuf7FMqTtcFkdCuSzIzfo7IDmPwc6nwRne_2yXrYOGq-oI-gkdu7GzZi7g=w1600-rj-l80-nu-e365 1600w\" data-loaded=\"true\" />\r\n<figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\">Heo Sung Tae with Jung Dong Won |&nbsp;<em>@heosungtae/Instagram</em></figcaption>\r\n</figure>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">But what does Heo himself find scary? The actor confessed one of his biggest phobias with a story from&nbsp;<em>Squid Game</em>&lsquo;s filming days. One scene in particular played on his fear so hard, it&rsquo;s stuck with him to this day&hellip;</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<figure id=\"attachment_1150222\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img class=\"lazyload-ph lazyload no-js-hide wp-image-1150222 size-full k-image\" style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/C45EQgAzGAKC2vCWghfIhUkLUSvLKF9HzjDNpvWtBiHagHoZc9VVQVMVHK8bG2iJ-FndumvuTzcdP7cTWfWMlKgVXYQ8fq2qQ7F9_5MDH05IHw=w32-fSoften=1,100,0-rp-e365\" sizes=\"(max-width: 945px) 100vw, 765px\" srcset=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/C45EQgAzGAKC2vCWghfIhUkLUSvLKF9HzjDNpvWtBiHagHoZc9VVQVMVHK8bG2iJ-FndumvuTzcdP7cTWfWMlKgVXYQ8fq2qQ7F9_5MDH05IHw=w480-rj-l80-nu-e365 480w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/C45EQgAzGAKC2vCWghfIhUkLUSvLKF9HzjDNpvWtBiHagHoZc9VVQVMVHK8bG2iJ-FndumvuTzcdP7cTWfWMlKgVXYQ8fq2qQ7F9_5MDH05IHw=w640-rj-l80-nu-e365 640w, https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/C45EQgAzGAKC2vCWghfIhUkLUSvLKF9HzjDNpvWtBiHagHoZc9VVQVMVHK8bG2iJ-FndumvuTzcdP7cTWfW